subtitleNullable: Face of Top Daily colored original illustrations from Pixiv in 2020
descriptionNullable:
### Dataset Description
The dataset contains face from [this dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/stevenevan99/pixiv-top-daily-illustration-2020). The top qualifying 96.7k images were collected, unordered on January 15, 2021.

The data was collected using the "Anime Face Detector" based on Faster-RCNN. The Documentation of the library can be found at [here](https://github.com/qhgz2013/anime-face-detector).

### License
All images in the dataset are copyright to their respective owners.
